### 1. Core Difference (Video ke hisab se)

| Aspect                  | **Flexbox**                                      | **Grid**                                          |
|-------------------------|--------------------------------------------------|---------------------------------------------------|
| Dimension               | **1D** (sirf ek direction – row ya column)       | **2D** (rows + columns dono control)              |
| Control karta hai       | Items ka behavior (grow, shrink, wrap)           | Overall structure (parent controls everything)    |
| Best jab                | Content apne aap adjust ho (intrinsic sizing)    | Fixed/rigid layout chahiye (explicit structure)   |
| Alignment               | Items ke beech spacing aur alignment bohot easy  | Both directions mein perfect alignment            |
| Spanning                | Mushkil                                          | Bahut asaan (`span`, `grid-column`)               |
| Responsive              | Media queries zyada lagte hain                   | `auto-fit` + `minmax()` se kam media queries     |

### 2. Kab Flexbox Use Karo? (When to choose Flexbox)

- Navigation menus (horizontal/vertical)
- Buttons group, icon + text alignment
- Card ke andar content align karna (title, description, button)
- Jab items ko **wrap** karna ho aur unka size content ke hisab se badle
- Centering ek single item ya group
- Jab aapko **items** ko control karna ho (na ki pura layout)

**Kevin ka Rule:** Agar aap soch rahe ho “yeh items ko aise align karna hai”, to Flexbox best hai.

### 3. Kab Grid Use Karo? (When to choose Grid)

- Poora page layout (header, sidebar, main, footer)
- Card grids / image galleries
- Jab aapko **columns aur rows** dono ko ek saath define karna ho
- Equal height columns chahiye
- Items ko span karna ho (ek item 2-3 columns cover kare)
- Complex 2D layouts (dashboard, holy grail)

**Kevin ka Rule:** Agar aap soch rahe ho “pura layout aisa hona chahiye”, to Grid best hai.

### 4. Best Practice – Mix Flexbox + Grid (Video ka Sabse Important Part)

```css
/* Outer structure → Grid */
.page {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 250px 1fr;
  grid-template-areas: "sidebar main";
  gap: 2rem;
}

/* Inner components → Flexbox */
.card {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  justify-content: space-between;
}
```

Yeh hybrid approach aaj kal sabse modern aur recommended hai.

### Quick Decision Table (Yaad rakhne ke liye)

| Aapka Sawal                              | Choose This     |
|------------------------------------------|-----------------|
| Sirf horizontal ya vertical alignment?   | Flexbox         |
| Pura page ya section ka structure?       | Grid            |
| Cards / Gallery bana rahe ho?            | Grid            |
| Nav menu, buttons, icons?                | Flexbox         |
| Items ko equal height chahiye?           | Grid            |
| Ek item ko multiple columns mein failana hai? | Grid       |
| Content-driven (items apne aap adjust hon) | Flexbox      |
| Layout-driven (parent decide kare)       | Grid            |
